version_description:
WATCH YOUR STEP! We can't count every breath you take or every move you make, but maybe we can count every step you take with our new Apple Watch app.

What's hot about the new watch app:
- Works without an iPhone
- Counts your steps in the background
- Lighter on your watch battery

Install now and do your Daily Boost!
